<XenonDocsLayout
  title="Accessibility"
  description="Keyboard operation, semantics, contrast, and motion."
  path="/xenon/accessibility"
>
  <p>Interactive controls use Base UI primitives with native semantics where available.</p>
  <p>Body text targets 4.5:1 contrast on canvas and surface backgrounds.</p>
  <p>Focus states use the accent outline defined in base styles.</p>
  <p>Motion respects <code>prefers-reduced-motion</code>.</p>
</XenonDocsLayout>
